Package: provoc
Type: Package
Title: package for analysis h5 from Vocus PTR-TOF-MS 
Version: 0.8.0
Author: Joris Huguenin <joris.huguenin@cefe.cnrs.fr>
Maintainer: Joris Huguenin <joris.huguenin@cefe.cnrs.fr>
Description: This package import h5 files from Vocus PTR-TOF-MS, compil all data in a list (sp in
              e.g) and from there analysis data. Much functions are create for measured the
              calibration of instruments or data, for calculated the area under the curve (AUC), for
              follow the AUC evolution in time, for maked a PCA or ICA analysis and for print graphs
              of spectra.
    Use four spaces when indenting paragraphs within the Description.
Depends: calibrate, carData, car, cluster, DescTools, dygraphs, ggplot2, hrbrthemes, ica,
         kableExtra, knitr, magrittr, MALDIquant, MASS, rhdf5, rnirs, scales, stringr, tidyverse,
         tinytex, viridis, zoo
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
